data.description: Beautifully maintained home inside and out. Brand new roof and gutters installed. Awesome large living room that is open to the kitchen area. Hardwood floors throughout. Extra room has stained concrete and can be used as a 4th bedroom, can be a den area, extra living room, or anything. Granite countertops with all new stainless appliances in the kitchen. Oven is a double oven so great for cooking and gatherings. Gas fireplace in living area. Gas heating and gas water heater. Master bedroom has onsuite bathroom. Extra storage in backyard. 21'x16' shop in back with own garage door to alley and extra garage. Small office off of dining room. Updated windows and doors. Nice, quiet neighborhood. Additions include: Concrete circle driveway, extended concrete driveway area to the north of the house, generator switch with a Generac plug, 50 amp rv plug on it's own breaker on the south side of the house. Wired for Vivint home security system. Home has new Nest controls to run the heating and air seamlessly. Newer water heater. The yard space has a lot of landscaping upgrades with flowers and plants.
